{"Sid":0,"Did":22257,"Id":"302989","Title":"邱曉光訪談錄","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/284a228d-eff0-41f7-bc59-c2a23efab876/p1.40-DSC_0369.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/ee7a8829-bd62-4a00-a38d-c89eeb585c38/p1.40-DSC_0002.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n邱曉光，民國40年3月13日出生，鳳山黃埔二村出生，其父為邱光第，民國7年1月10日出生，四川省榮縣人。\n\n邱光第為孫立人將軍新一軍的部屬，擔任陸軍通信職。早期跟著孫立人將軍征戰緬甸、雲南等地，抗戰結束後，又隨著孫立人將軍來臺練兵，而遷來臺灣。父親在孫立人案的時候因剛好於空軍受訓，而險些受到牽連。長大後的受訪者，擔任林園石化園區工程師，後又出國進修，並在國外工作，近些年才回到臺灣定居。\n\n邱曉光為來臺第二代，小時候長期居住於黃埔新村，亦對於新村的保存，有著期許。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"NULL","Keyword_Latitude":"NULL","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/D714D633-4E6C-41D4-A985-EB871CB278D4","Original_Identifier":"302989","Keyword_Subject_1":"社會與政治","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"孫立人 / 黃埔新村 / 新一軍","dates":"採訪時間 / 2014/01/28","LastUpdateTime":"2020/01/04 16:35:04","Creator":"顧超光、莊榮華","publisher":"","mediaType":"文件","language":"","timelines":"戰後時期 (1945~)","city":"","address":"","lng":"","lat":"","contributors":"","contributor":"顧超光、張岳茹","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"高雄市政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/5ed9c3e5-520b-47ea-b905-135e462c6612/p1.40-DSC_0369.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/4186247b-d029-46d0-b938-23d549fad01f/p1.40-DSC_0002.jpg"}}